---
title: Greek Inspired Veggie Kofta Loaded Flatbreads with Oregano Chips, Feta and Honey Yoghurt
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Greek Inspired Veggie Kofta Loaded Flatbreads are perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.
